version_description: All of these version go to the wrong chord in the verses--they go to the relative major (G) of the actual chord being sounded (Em)...This was also put together after watching a live performance of the band in which one of their guitarists plays the song with a capo on the third fret which makes the arrangement much more intuitive for beginners (F major is weird)
None of the rest have all the correct chords or lyrics... some even mistake bass parts for guitar.
